description:
THE DANGEROUS BROTHERS PRESENT: &quot;WORLD OF DANGER&quot; is a series of short sketches from the British SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE featuring Sir Richard Dangerous (Rik Mayall) and Lady Adrian Dangerous (Adrian Edmondson) as a couple of guys (who may or may not really be brothers) trying to entertain us with dangerous stunts. Essentially it's just Rik and Ade doing what they do best... beating the shit out of each other for our amusement. 
It also boasts memorable stints by Jennifer Saunders, Stephen Fry and Hugh Laurie. 
The sketches were filmed in 1986, long before BOTTOM came along. This download also includes an original sketch performed on a show called BOOM BOOM OUT GO THE LIGHTS back in 1981, shortly before THE YOUNG ONES came along.

